{
  "stem": "5758.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "The political prisoners had a red triangle-- some with F from France, or G from-- D from Deutschland, from Germany, and-- and political prisoners.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Anyhow, we went-- the one fellow came to us with a green triangle and said, I am your capo.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "You're going to work under me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And you will follow my instructions.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Whoever doesn't follow my instructions will be slaughtered, will be hit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And I will see to it that you work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And I am the-- I am your boss.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I am your-- your leader, and you have to follow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "You are going to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] And we marched out-- out of the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And we heard the music playing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "It was an orchestra.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "As we marched out to work, we had to greet the SS by-- by putting our hats, caps off their head, because the capo shouted, mutzen auf!",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "Auf!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "So we had to take the hat off in front of the SS and march out in even step.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And we walked from somewhere around 15 minutes and went to a very big factory where they-- where [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there were all these people in uniform, in striped uniform, working.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "We saw them digging roads.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "We saw them carrying a heavy metal thing on their back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And we were told that we are the cement commando.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "We had to carry 50 kilo cement bags from our-- from a train to a factory.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And we had to-- this is what we did all day long.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And if we didn't walk fast enough, we were hit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And it-- it was something that a lot of people just could not stand.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Sometimes the capo did hit us, especially when he saw some SS men coming.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
